<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-80-0315 </DOCNO><TEXT>The purpose of this incentive report is to present a model incentive andcompensation package and to examine the factors that might be addressedin implementing a host state incentive and compensation program. Thepackage is intended to be available to a community and state that volunteersor that is designated by the Commission to host a radioactive waste disposalfacility. This report incorporates comments received from the Commissionon a draft version of the report dated February 28, 1986. 10 refs., 4tabs.</TEXT></DOC>